ovement that you can control yourself and no timeout will be applied. Selecting motion at lower speeds will be interpreted as requiring finer control and the automatic timeout will be invoked.
\par }\pard \s30\qj \li540\ri0\sa180\widctlpar\nooverflow\faroman\rin0\lin540\itap0\pararsid1386006 {\b\insrsid1386006 Track Motion \endash }{\insrsid1386006  This and the following four options are used with
