\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6177204 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}\pard \s27\qj \fi-357\li714\ri0\sa180\widctlpar\tx720\nooverflow\faroman\ls4\rin0\lin714\itap0\pararsid6177204 {\insrsid6177204 FEATURE 
\endash  The zmtrigger.pl script has been compl
eted revamped to support both incoming and outgoing triggers. Certain example triggers and connections have been included in the trigger modules but this is intended to be an example only and to provide a basis for users to customise and add their own fun
ctionality. Users will also be able to contribute modules tailored to specific external systems.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6177204 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}\pard \s27\qj \fi-357\li714\ri0\sa180\widctlpar\tx720\nooverflow\faroman\ls4\rin0\lin714\itap0\pararsid6177204 {\insrsid6177204 FEATURE 
\endash  More configuration has been moved to the zm.conf file. All components now use this file for initial configuration. Scripts may also use a local copy, in the same directory, to allow overrides etc.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8259013 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}{\insrsid8259013 FEATURE \endash  The zmconfig.pl script is no more! Building now only requires the \lquote configure\rquote 
 step and then make etc. Database parameters can be supplied to the configure script.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8259013 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  The configure script now includes more system suitability checks including checks for required and optional perl modules.

\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8259013 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  All libjpeg output is now trapped and handled}{\insrsid5205357  as regular format debug}{\insrsid8259013 .
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8259013 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  Some jpeg data is cached on first use instead of being regenerated each time. This should 
speed up jpeg handling to some degree.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8259013 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  Event data can be optionally saved to COM fields in the jpeg file header.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8259013 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  A system summary command has been added to zmu.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8259013 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  Filtering can now be done on the event id field.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8259013 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  Filtering can now be done on the event description field.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6237187 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}{\insrsid6237187 FEATURE \endash  The \lquote check all\rquote  on event lists etc is now a toggle checkbox.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6237187 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  In Mocord mode, events can now be forced to close when the event has reached the section length
 even if an alarm is in progress. Previously this would have resulted in an extended event.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6237187 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  The \lquote groups\rquote  view has been overhauled and rationalised.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6237187 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  A default event replay rate has been added.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6237187 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  Videos can now be created from filters.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6237187 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  There is now a separate auto-execute checkbox from filters to allow definition of a script but not exe
cution if this is not desired.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6237187 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}\pard \s27\qj \fi-357\li714\ri0\sa180\widctlpar\tx720\nooverflow\faroman\ls4\rin0\lin714\itap0\pararsid6177204 {\insrsid6237187 FEATURE 
\endash  When filters are loaded, a hint appears to indicate what automatic function options they have been saved with.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6177204 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}\pard \s27\qj \fi-357\li714\ri0\sa180\widctlpar\tx720\nooverflow\faroman\ls4\rin0\lin714\itap0\pararsid6177204 {\insrsid6177204 FEATURE 
\endash  Improved the behaviour of the automatic }{\insrsid6237187 PTZ }{\insrsid6177204 stop feature when using Pelco type PTZ cameras.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid6237187 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}\pard \s27\qj \fi-357\li714\ri0\sa180\widctlpar\tx720\nooverflow\faroman\ls4\rin0\lin714\itap0\pararsid6177204 {\insrsid6237187 FEATURE 
\endash  The configure script now allows an option to compile all debug out from the binaries.}{\insrsid6177204 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid4470415 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}{\insrsid4470415 FEATURE \endash  The configure script now takes a generic \lquote extra libs\rquote 
 option to allow specification of any extra libraries that may be required for compilation due to additional ffmpeg options etc. The mp3lame option has been removed.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid4470415 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  Mime support for streaming has been enhanced to 
allow easy configuration of additional formats of data streaming. The streaming daemons themselves have also been improved to support the generation of other stream formats.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid4470415 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  The handling of video viewing via the \lquote video\rquote 
 view has been improved to allow embedded viewing of videos as well as easy saving locally.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid4470415 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  The alarm sound that can be configured to play when viewing a monitor with a current alarm has now been improved 
to not depend on the refreshing of the status which resulted in clipped audio.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid7087554 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}{\insrsid7087554 FEATURE \endash  Script debug now follows the same format as all debug and uses the syslog facility. This means that }{
\insrsid5205357 all important messages go into the /var/log/messages file (or equivalent). This can be modified by redirecting the local1 facility in syslog.conf to go elsewhere, or be ignored, if so desired.}{\insrsid7087554 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid5205357 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}{\insrsid5205357 FEATURE \endash  A new raw streaming format has been added for live monitor streams. This produces a low 
cpu impact raw rgb feed.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid5205357 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  A zm.pid file is now placed in /var/run/zm when ZoneMinder is running, and removed when stopped. This can be used 
by other elements to check the status of ZoneMinder. The pid in the file is that of the master zmdc.pl server instance.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid5205357 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  The continuous/triggered settings for monitors have now been removed. 
They have been replaced by an Enabled flag that indicates whether a monitor is actually doing the task assigned to it. This can be used by scripts to disable or enable monitors depending 
on external triggers without having to change the Function or start and stop daemons. The state of this flag is now saved in \lquote run states\rquote  to allow ZoneMinder to be started with some monitors initially disabled.
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid5205357 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}FEATURE \endash  Restructured zmfilter.pl to better handle filters and ensure that auto functions are perf}{\insrsid13127531 
ormed in a logical sequence (e.g. not deleted before being archived).}{\insrsid5205357 
\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid13127531 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}{\insrsid13127531 FEATURE \endash  Added link to Zones configuration to the live watch view.
