\par {\listtext\pard\plain\s27 \f2\fs20\lang2057\langfe1033\langfenp1033\insrsid8594609 \hich\af2\dbch\af0\loch\f2 o\tab}}{\insrsid8594609 FEATURE \endash  When motion is detected the centre of the region of motion is 
